      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大豆价格如此便宜，连竞争对手阿根廷都在购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/us-soy-is-so-cheap-that-even-rival-argentina-is-buying-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷是全球最大的加工豆粕和豆油出口国，由于美国豆价下滑，阿根廷将自 2019 年以来首次从美国进口整豆，目前美国豆价已降至全球最便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/us-soy-is-so-cheap-that-even-rival-argentina-is-buying-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
